            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.Excitation Functions For (P,D),(P,P) And",
                " (P,P') Have Been Taken Near the Zr-96(P,N)Nb-96",
                "Threshold of the Excitated State Which is the Analogue",
